{"tid":2074463,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"邵家臻：劉家棟親筆字條呼籲社工界勿被嚇怕","createTime":"2020-06-22T06:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T13:51:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79f58564ae2c604f3819ffe68cd17feef218085b","tid":2074463,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533406-20200622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533406-20200622.htm&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e870992a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533406-20200622.htm&h=e7eb8cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533406-20200622.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n社福界立法會議員邵家臻說，早前探望因阻差辦公罪成被判囚1年的「社工復興運動」成員劉家棟。對方親筆字條表示，拘捕及裁決沒有令他退縮，又呼籲同行不用因此被嚇怕。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻說，今次裁決令整個社工界感到憤怒，認為判刑過份及帶有惡意，是針對整個社工界。業界亦擔心社工捍衛人道公義的工作，是否能夠繼續。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻強調，人道工作是社工的天職，不少機構工會和組織發出聲明支持劉家棟，國際上亦有不少學者關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n劉家棟被指去年7月27日的元朗警民衝突中，在警方作出驅散行動時，以身體擋在警員前面。"},{"pid":"7ee672974d09843c2419dbbbf8de922b8649a14b","tid":2074463,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d5e05a02acc4e9d1f13dab0587391444552d88","tid":2074463,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0223324090bc36be883cd85e06127ab24557296","tid":2074463,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}